data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. A true gem, this residence boasts multitudes of upgrades making it a home that has had all the big (and small) renovations already done.  Located in the heart of a great family neighborhood, this home will impress you with the upgrades and attention to detail.  As you approach, the curb appeal is undeniable, with a NEW roof installed in 2022, offering not just aesthetic appeal but also the peace of mind that comes with a recent upgrade. The allure continues with ALL NEW HURRICANE RATED WINDOWS AND DOORS, a tasteful touch implemented in 2018, providing lower utility bills and energy efficiency.  The NEW air conditioning, along with NEW ductwork and a UV LIGHT system installed in 2022 ensuring your comfort and well-being year-round. The NEW garage door opener in 2021 and oversized THREE CAR GARAGE provides additional storage. All NEW smoke detectors installed in 2022, NEW water filtration/water softening system added in 2021 and a NEWER water tank installed in 2016. The kitchen showcases NEWER stainless range and microwave, promising both functionality and style.  Open kitchen to family room offers large living with multiple (NEW) sliding glass doors. Long countertops for after school snacks and conversation or socializing with guests and family.  Three way split floor plan gives everyone the space and privacy they need.  The attention to detail extends to the exterior, where a wood deck wraps around a tree in the expansive backyard—a perfect spot for relaxation and entertaining. The large fully fenced backyard not only offers privacy but also serves as a canvas for your gardening aspirations or a playground for family activities, human and furry. Park with ease in the THREE car garage, a rare find that adds practicality to your daily routine. This community boasts LOW HOA FEES, ensuring you enjoy the benefits of a well-maintained community without breaking the bank. Additionally, relish the relief of LOW ELECTRIC BILLS, because of the new windows, doors and roof.  Community features a gorgeous resort-style pool, park, two playgrounds, basketball court and soccer field, two dog parks and tennis courts.  NO CDD and LOW HOA fees. The convenient location is a key highlight, with proximity to Brandon, I75, I4, downtown and Tampa International Airport. This home is not just a dwelling; it's a lifestyle upgrade, offering a harmonious blend of modern amenities and the warmth of a welcoming neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to call this house your home.
